Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.03,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nami's been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:34.53,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:41.43,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They were huge, but I still didn't notice them until they were right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.24,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,First it's centaurs, now it's beastmen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.63,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,This island's crawling with weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:51.71,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Maybe they're testing us for weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:56.43,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So, they didn't come to rescue Brown-gator?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:03:01.12,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Their true objective seemed to be the children,\Nand our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:06.28,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,But it sounded like Master hired them to silence Brownbeard first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:07.57,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Even though they're supposed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.86,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Even though Brownbeard admired Master so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:15.13,Flashbacks,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Master is the kind-hearted god of salvation.{cp from 591, which is slight rewording of 589}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:19.92,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Luffy, Master really is a twisted individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:25.29,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I would never let the children go back\Nto such a cruel person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.37,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm also worried about Nami-Franky, who got kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.87,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Who knows what they could be doing to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're definitely getting her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll leave the kids to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.95,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hold it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.16,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It was my body that they took.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.94,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Chopper, I can't fight in this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.57,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Gimme some of those beans that you use to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.19,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The beans that make you a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:52.80,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Beans?  The Rumble Ball is a dangerous drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It'd probably be impossible for you to control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:04:00.08,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'll super-overcome that with fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:01.56,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and gimme 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.11,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Okay, but just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:07.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Got it?  You can only be a monster for three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.26,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,After that, you won't be able to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.29,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,If possible, just use Kung-fu Point which I showed you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.93,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Vvvvvvvvuper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.93,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.04,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's go, Franky.  This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.52,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why are you attacking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.23,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's no good!  I knew he'd go berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:53.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So... what was Franky planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:59.19,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,After the rampage he won't be able to move,\Nso I don't think he'll be much help... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.61,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,He's just going to be in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.89,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,544)\fad(500,0)}Caesar's Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.84,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I don't know where he got it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:14.72,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,but it seems that the metal man Franky\Ninstalled one of Vegapunk's lasers into his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:21.95,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,After we dissect him and take the laser system, there'll be no other use for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.01,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Might as well throw him in the incinerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.92,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:29.25,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And can you tell me what happened\Nto those stupid Marines who came to take a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.08,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.08,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,The battle has become quite chaotic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:37.72,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,So... you're saying that you can't handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.69,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:44.23,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, I know just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.51,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.92,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,We are fighting the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:06:01.20,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,This is a perfect situation to put {\i1}him{\i0} to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.50,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, that's good.  Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:13.19,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Immediately contact the centaurs that are out on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:13.94,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.27,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And tell the rest of the soldiers to use this time to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.56,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,If they want to live, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:29.39,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(500,500)}Laboratory - Far Side of the Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.02,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lemme go!  Lemme go, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.70,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What are you perverts doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.58,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Why are you kidnapping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:41.96,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Although I am cute, and proportioned,\Nso I understand why you would {\i1}want{\i0} to kidnap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.59,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,What is this man saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.68,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,He must be queer.  Pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:49.91,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.85,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.49,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're gonna get beaten to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:07:00.04,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Shut up now.  People who talk too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.67,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,are not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:06.84,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,But apparently,\Nthe weapon that's built into your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.26,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.67,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,And when we hand you over to Master,\Nthe reward will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.80,Main,Scotch+Rock,0,0,0,,{\i1}so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:25.25,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(500,0)}Rock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.52,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(500,0)}Scotch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:33.40,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,441)\fad(500,0)}{\fscx250}-{\r} Hit Men of Snowy Mountain {\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:33.40,captions_soft,Text2,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,482)\fad(500,0)}Yeti Cool Brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.27,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,But it's really cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.52,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Yeah, our bodies are too cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.43,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Put some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:40.16,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,With the difference in size between us,\Nthese rifles are like cannons to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.14,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,We have poison-gas bullets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.89,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,And if we don't show ourselves\Nthen there's no way to defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:48.91,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,You got friends coming?  Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.44,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,We arranged for them to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:56.25,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,It's only natural that they'll follow our footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Footsteps!  Footsteps!  Man, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's so easy to see where they're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:15.60,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!  Franky!  I said to cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.41,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The footsteps disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:30.89,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:34.40,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy?  And Chopper... No, that's Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:40.11,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Watch out!  There are enemies here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.35,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Let's go, Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.44,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:50.13,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,He must be pretty thick\Nif he didn't even notice the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.92,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There's spikes below!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.40,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,This is almost too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.33,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,The ice spikes will pierce him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.70,Note,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Color of Arms - Hardening
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.27,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.49,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,I guess the normal tricks won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.92,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:36.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Using this technique to deflect attacks\Nin random directions isn't much good in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:39.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Rayleigh taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:43.44,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Instead, turn it into a counterattack by sending\Nevery bullet back at your enemy with double power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.85,Note,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Gun Salute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.31,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.96,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I said cut it out, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.39,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Why is {\i1}he{\i0}{\fscx125} {\r}the one giving you the most trouble here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.34,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Now I'm hot and bothered.\NThey're fighting amongst themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.72,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,They're underestimating us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.07,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.97,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,I'll show you! The frozen mountain has all kinds of weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:33.59,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Look out!  The frozen summit's falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy!  Franky!  Look up!  Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.33,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,You won't be able to dodge\Nthat block of ice after I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.58,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,They're attacking from the sides!  Enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:48.71,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,This KYP gas-bullet will knock you out instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.84,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Die, just like your other friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.28,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,He did something useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.84,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Great job, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.59,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the strongest attack you've used today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.22,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:38.50,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Dammit!  Sorry, Franky-Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.07,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll have Chopper look at your injuries later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.10,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:47.72,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,I thought we told you.\NThe mountain is our playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.28,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,It's impossible to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.86,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:58.07,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,He doesn't give up.  But he can't match my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.93,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's like a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:04.94,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:22.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Dammit.  The mountain's huge,\Nso if he gets away then it'll be impossible to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.15,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:35.38,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Trafalgar Law, the freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:40.36,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I ran into you.  Right now, Straw Hat Luffy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:11.57,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.71,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.11,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Wait... Hey, you!  Gimme my body back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.54,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.46,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:54.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Traf!  So you saved Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.38,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:03.55,Main,Law,0,0,0,,There's something\NI'd like to discuss with you, Straw-Hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:09.80,Main,Law,0,0,0,,It may have been just a coincidence that you came to this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:17.73,Main,Law,0,0,0,,but there's actually a {\i1}key{\i0}{\fscx125} {\r}hidden here.  One with\Nthe power to throw the entire New World into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:22.59,Main,Law,0,0,0,,There are two ways to survive in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:28.25,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Either be protected by one of the Four Emperors,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:30.14,Main,Law,0,0,0,,or fight all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:37.17,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You're not the kind of guy\Nwho'll serve under someone else, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That's right.  I prefer being the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:45.80,Main,Law,0,0,0,,In that case, form an alliance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.28,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If you and I work together, we might be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:04.39,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I've got a plan to dethrone one of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:12.06,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:17.61,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting that if we work together\Nwe could defeat one of the Four Emperors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:21.61,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!  I don't know what you're after, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:24.89,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy, don't fall for his fast talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:33.39,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I didn't say we'd be able to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:38.35,Main,Law,0,0,0,,But if we play our cards right\Nwe should eventually be able to create an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.91,Main,Law,0,0,0,,What do you say, Straw-Hatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:47.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Which one of the Four Emperors are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.13,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Hold on, Luffy!  Why are you listening to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.80,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You can't trust someone like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:19.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:22.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Okay!  We're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.23,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:29.43,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,542)}Straw Hat Pirates' Temporary Shelter{lit. evacuation point--not temporary}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:29.43,Main,Usopp+Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:34.29,Main,Usopp+Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're forming an alliance with the Heart Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:40.82,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You just went to get Nami back,\Nso how did it come to such a crazy deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Like I said{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:48.47,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I won't be able to sleep at night if we form an alliance with such an enigmatic, unpredictable bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.96,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Come on Luffy, everybody's against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:55.10,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We don't have to do it.\NThere's no reason to do something this dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.16,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We should continue our voyage at our own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:02.69,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That's right, Luffy!\NIt's far too soon to try to take on the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.29,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There's no way we could fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.25,Main,Law,0,0,0,,So what about this raccoon dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.63,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm not a raccoon dog anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:11.82,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Whaa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.79,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:18.03,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,S-Super...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.26,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.60,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.16,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I'll follow your decision, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:32.37,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,pirate alliances and betrayal go hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:36.00,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,They might not be suited\Nfor someone as overly trusting as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, you gonna betray me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.10,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.90,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey!  Try to be a little skeptical!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:45.61,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Anyway,\NI think a pirate alliance sounds like a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:49.09,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I think Traf's a good guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,but even if he isn't, there's no need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:56.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You guys have trained a lot in the past two years\Nand can back me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.66,Main,All,0,0,0,,Whaaa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:00.80,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Luffy, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:05.37,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Oh, cut it out!  It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:09.88,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey, you can super-rely on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:14.15,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We do manage to help out every now and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.24,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,but it's not like we're happy, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:20.87,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A-Alright then, Luffy!  You can rely on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:24.11,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If Zoro and the others chicken out,\NI will convince them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:42.24,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'm back!  Back in my perfect body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:44.89,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Yep, being me is best for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.72,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,That's great, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.64,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I hope you never wind up back in Chopper's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.64,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.79,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.19,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.30,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,But how could you leave my body all broken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.48,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What the hell were you thinking,\Ntreating other people's bodies like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:08.83,Main,Luffy+Franky,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.76,Main,Luffy+Franky,0,0,0,,It's all his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:14.79,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What?!\NYou were the one rampaging in Chopper's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.53,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,My only choice was to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:20.94,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But still, you didn't have to use an attack powerful enough to take out the kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.23,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You're both just as bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.33,Main,Luffy+Frank,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.15,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Isn't it enough just to be in your own body, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:31.38,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one who has to bear this pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.96,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,First Franky's body and now Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:37.66,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Don't laugh at others' expense!  I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.11,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:45.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We have Chopper and Franky's bodies,\Nso their souls can return to the right places...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,but Sanji took your body to search for the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:53.81,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Your soul was left over,\Nso it had to go into Sanji's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.09,Main,Nami,0,0,0,, Can't you do anything?  Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.46,Main,Law,0,0,0,,It's impossible without a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.83,Main,Law,0,0,0,,So these are the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.63,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wanna save these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.70,Main,Law,0,0,0,,They're more trouble than they're worth.  Leave 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.59,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Apparently they're all addicted to drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.73,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We know that!  I examined them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:23.03,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That's why I want to take them back to their homes, but it'll take time to get the drug out of their system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.57,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,And they've been turned into giants too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:29.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What a terrible experiment they performed on them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:34.73,Main,Law,0,0,0,,They've been researching\Nhow to turn humans into giants for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.83,Main,Law,0,0,0,,The project was run by the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.25,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The Government?  Why would they do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.63,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Most likely to make soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:49.51,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Nobody could stand against the Government\Nif they turned all of their soldiers into giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:58.15,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If Caesar successfully perfects the process\Nthen he would trump the Government and Vegapunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.42,Main,Law,0,0,0,,but of course it isn't an easy thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.48,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You really want to save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.20,Main,Law,0,0,0,,They're just some random kids from here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.83,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Yes.  Maybe we've never met\Nor even seen these kids before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.42,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,but the kids cried and begged that we save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:21.33,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Master may have done a good job\Nof tricking them to bring them here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:26.14,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,but some of the older children are already realizing that this facility isn't exactly what it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:35.98,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Until I make sure that these kids are safe,\NI will never leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.74,Main,Law,0,0,0,,So, are you planning to stay here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:41.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We don't leave anybody behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:44.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami and Chopper want to do it,\Nso I'll help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:49.03,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, and Sanji went to put the samurai back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:52.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If you're going to be allied with us\Nthen you gotta help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.82,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Jeez, I knew you had no idea what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.93,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,The "alliance" he asked you to form...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:08.45,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,only means that we're working together for the\Nsole purpose of achieving a certain objective, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:09.51,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:14.73,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That's what you meant, but when Luffy\Nhears the word "alliance" he thinks of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:16.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Like friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:20.52,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If you thought you could get him to follow some plan,\Nthat isn't gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:21.96,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:27.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Once he gets some wild idea, he won't budge.\NThat's the problem with Luffy.  It's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:31.03,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,In terms of self-centered stubbornness, Luffy's on par with the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.45,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Wow, that sounds terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:38.95,Main,Law,0,0,0,,But what your crew member is currently trying to do\Nhas absolutely nothing to do with our{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:42.78,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Hey!  Don't flick boogers on me, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.07,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.81,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I can't even dodge when I'm like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:48.84,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:53.43,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.  We don't have time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:57.06,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You guys can take care of the samurai yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.94,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I'll investigate the drug\Nthat was administered to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:02.34,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Which one of you is the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:06.18,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Come with me.  We'll have to distract Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.23,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Okay, this should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:15.70,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sorry.  I can't move right now so I'll have to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:22.41,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Don't drop him, Traf!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:25.02,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sorry... can't stop... laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.87,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Super-cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:30.57,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:31.51,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:42.01,Main,Law,0,0,0,,It should be clear\Nfrom the actions of the two assassins...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:49.88,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Caesaro plans to kill both you and White Hunter's G-5,\Nand then take the kids back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:55.96,Main,Law,0,0,0,,He'll keep coming until he gets what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:24:01.61,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Four years ago, as a former Government scientist, he was judged a criminal after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:06.79,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If word gets out that there are people on this island, which is supposed to be off-limits to everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:10.31,Main,Law,0,0,0,,then he'll lose this perfect hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.31,0:24:12.93,Main,Law,0,0,0,,That's why he'll do everything he can to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.71,0:24:16.21,Main,Law,0,0,0,,He has a bounty of 300 million beli.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:21.69,Main,Law,0,0,0,,He possesses weapons of mass destruction as well as\Nthe powers of the Gas Gas Fruit, a logia-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.69,0:24:24.21,Main,Law,0,0,0,,That's the Caesar Clown we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.49,0:24:28.10,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,300 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.75,0:24:32.05,Main,Law,0,0,0,,People who can't wield haki\Nshould definitely stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:33.81,Main,Law,0,0,0,,He isn't your average scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.23,0:24:37.88,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Our haki-users are me, Zoro, and Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.53,0:24:40.05,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,And you, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:41.71,Main,Law,0,0,0,,That should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:44.51,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I'll head to the laboratory first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.51,0:24:49.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Then when we get there,\Nwe'll all kidnap Master together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.33,0:24:50.94,Main,Law,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:54.34,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,But... what do you mean by kidnap?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.34,0:24:58.65,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,For ransom?  But wouldn't Master have the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.65,0:25:01.21,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If you kidnap him, who's going to pay us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.21,0:25:04.47,Main,Law,0,0,0,,The objective isn't money.  It's confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.16,0:25:07.23,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:08.64,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.64,0:25:13.68,Main,Law,0,0,0,,There's no point in talking about it, until we succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.29,0:25:18.01,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Anyways, focus on capturing Caesar Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.01,0:25:19.95,Main,Law,0,0,0,,It won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.45,0:25:26.14,Main,Law,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\NI'll lay out the entire plan to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.14,0:25:30.56,Main,Law,0,0,0,,But once we succeed in capturing Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:34.05,Main,Law,0,0,0,,the situation's naturally going to be chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.05,0:25:37.13,Main,Law,0,0,0,,When that happens, there's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.97,0:25:43.53,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I guess this is our last chance to change our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.53,0:25:45.69,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's fine.  I'll work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.43,0:25:49.99,Main,Law,0,0,0,,In that case, I also accept your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.80,0:25:53.57,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Make sure to convince the rest of your crew as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.57,0:25:55.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.08,0:26:02.11,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,542)\fad(500,0)}Caesar Clown's Laboratory - Main Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.14,0:26:05.17,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Take this!  You damn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.01,0:26:11.44,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Iron-joint Smoodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:14.26,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Fein Bock the Gourd!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.05,0:26:20.62,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Chappe the Rope-puller!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.62,0:26:22.12,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:26.06,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,There's no doubt, these are all former prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.06,0:26:27.95,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Though their bodies have been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.85,0:26:35.19,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.59,0:26:40.96,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,The accident report from four years ago said that none of the prisoners survived.  Was that a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:44.64,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Smo-san, who are these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:47.31,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.31,0:26:50.74,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Just focus on drawing the enemy inland for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.47,0:26:58.72,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,We {\i1}will{\i0} get on board that ship,\Nand set sail to make our report!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.19,0:27:14.46,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Master, the Snail Phone's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.04,0:27:18.06,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,No need to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.06,0:27:20.84,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,They're going to say, "We opened the door."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.59,0:27:24.37,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And then, "Something came out of it."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:28.42,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,"Some of our men died.  Save us."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.42,0:27:30.23,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And then screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.23,0:27:31.71,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,It's hard on the ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.17,0:27:36.52,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,We have more than enough people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.52,0:27:39.37,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,We can always capture more test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.94,0:27:54.64,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?!  Master!  Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.18,0:27:58.25,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.25,0:28:02.55,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,This is the Burning Lands!\NWe opened the door, just like you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.71,0:28:08.18,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,It's no use!  Master isn't answering!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.75,0:28:09.86,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.86,0:28:13.44,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,What the hell is that thing\Nthat came out of the warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.35,0:28:17.43,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,We've already lost too many men.  Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.71,0:28:51.07,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,It's as big as a mountain!  What the hell is that blob?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.05,0:29:19.80,Main,Gotaur,0,0,0,,It's right behind us!  Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.80,0:29:22.11,Main,Rocktaur,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.87,0:29:40.11,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Let me introduce my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.01,0:29:45.97,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,It's an extremely rare life-form, a slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.92,0:29:50.68,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Ma...ster...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:57.22,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,No one will make it off this island alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.32,0:30:12.24,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,How's it feel to be free after so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.24,0:30:14.49,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Smiley!
